Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道「低級趣味」這個詞嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂前衛藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常難以被愚昧的大眾所接受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被當作令人不快的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說你做的太過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也是 在那個什麼「Dog Race Show」裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉了多少人!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連不是死刑犯的犯人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那簡直就是公開屠殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的庇護也是有極限的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們見所長 和你已經沒法談下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老頭不過是個行屍走肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我老老實實地搾取補助金就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了將「原罪」 Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續封印在這座「死囚樂園」裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:26.62,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,505)\pos(990,550)\blur1}#03   G 棟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃 丸太覺得如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機會再一起吃點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就要被執行死刑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的Race太嚇人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體處理班都總動員了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要中途退出 也很難做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得那麼誇張 卻沒優勝者 簡直莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我沒參加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個Race的難度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用下半身想都知道有蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是參加了 想必現在也已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個新人 五十嵐丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為他參加了才變成那樣的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致美美的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有留遺書的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以決定寫給美美父親您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許您不會相信我所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是殺了美美和山炸排 還有班裡其它人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就要被執行死刑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你是這間囚室的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我們是室友 真是太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找你噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是「Candy」?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我撞倒了你 才弄丟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我需要負責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是總算弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你一定要收下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下 我就還能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 羊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一輩子都不會忘記你的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情不這麼發展 我才為難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我不惜受重傷才弄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那個創辦人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟為何對這傢伙那麼執著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我監視這次來的新人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然報酬是不會虧待你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼細節都可以 只要有什麼動作或是變化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來向我報告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要什麼說明嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只需要CastPoint
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的模範囚犯已經沒有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 籠絡了他 沒什麼壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 難吃的傳聞可是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 去吃點什麼清清口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Mather Goose System」停止運行了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(587,663)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}原罪脫逃?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 創辦人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢修時 貌似發生了原因不明的error
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前0.1秒也好 快給我重啟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(554,661)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}在原罪笑出來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 沒錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買單啦 作為友誼的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 真是把全班同學都殺了的（瘋子）嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 越是這種傢伙就越不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想起了以前的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許 那時 我真的很快樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 丸太 沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅衣…男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍捲風? 爆炸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 究竟怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來殺我的朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是「罪之枝」的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個混蛋!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從手裡射出了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑 混蛋 站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Mather Goose System」修復
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}確認了原罪的波動干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(598,659)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(504,661)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}原罪捕獲部隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲 這果然不是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的住人誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 這報酬太少了 那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個紅色的傢伙也是 這群怪物怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 這血肉歡騰的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的「死囚樂園」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊啊啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在睡 我不留神把你的點心也吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說庭院裡發生了恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是恐怖襲擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我 突然胸口刺痛 然後用了奇怪的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那傢伙類似的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 紅衣男 那混蛋就在這所監獄裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我能射出那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅衣…男?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 那時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼 我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的 全身戴滿了奇怪束縛器具的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 以前也有見過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年前 一個傢伙像那樣 使出了詭異的龍卷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把工廠的牆都吹跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那傢伙現在還被關在一個叫G棟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G棟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅衣男 就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的朋友都殺掉了的 那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「利落」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於之前的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對外聲稱是激進派人權保護團體所策劃的炸彈襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那犯人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉木創辦人稱 「此案已結」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不清楚那隻老狐狸想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我另有線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要參考人 就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5580號 是那個孩子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙有種奇怪的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不叫人聯想到他帶有什麼強力的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 蒔名看守長 這也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非這武器藏在他體內
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的榮耀就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維護這座死囚樂園的安全和秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一味地得過且過消極度日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動代號是「All Red」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迅速到位地將其捉拿歸案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 看守長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不會是要用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急狀態下使用代號的意義 不懂麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讓我們停止無謂的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而更迅速地完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急封鎖各處設施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安保裝置「Necro Macro」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,序列鎖 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認密碼 2DOD 7785
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前曾因一名囚犯鬧事而使用過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因此造成死傷24人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 將它視為不可使用之物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是擔心那孩子會導致更多的犧牲者?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:50.26,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在下達禁止外出令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.43,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}所有的工作人員和服刑者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.81,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}請迅速回到自己的房間和監牢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.90,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}保持待命 直至緊急狀態解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.90,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}此外 5580號請即刻前來報到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒔名長官也真是的 太小題大做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太要是變成廢品的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個監視者要如何負責呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹見羊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能有能力去照看那些怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅斗篷男人已經被順利逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為丸太是被邀請前往真正死囚樂園的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要好好地對他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也覺得這麼做不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.32,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}5580號請即刻前來報到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:49.82,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}重複5580號請即刻前來報道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5580號 是在叫我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丸太 你怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是說這話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 是跑步比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是因為啟用了最高級的安保措施
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你要是無視報到命令的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會像我一樣被懲罰的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後別再給我出問題了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊 對不起 我趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在比賽跑步喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊你也看到了吧 那個紅衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那種奇怪的能力把我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我所有朋友一個不留地都殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說 這裡的犯人逃出去殺人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事怎麼可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說那傢伙在G棟的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我 必須過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G棟? 沒有這個地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這裡監牢的構造 只有A到F的六個部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 G棟什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 不說這個了 你還是快去報到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G棟?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G那裡我能去哦 我知道有條捷徑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的麼 白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你撅什麼嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的話 就告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓 安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保安機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是來抓你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白 捷徑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我搞不懂你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白醬?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微推一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能從這裡去很多地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微?…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認目標為5580號和9061號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小偷也在一起麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機器人要殺了我們麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些看守打算幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 這裡！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 停下了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊 你剛才做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手賤是我的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手賤?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從剛才開始就生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是G棟?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅衣男就在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去目標反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Necro Macro」也失去反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒔名看守長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能全都突然消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示在這死囚樂園中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在不屬於我管轄的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經來到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊 白 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把毫無關係的你們倆扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點沒錯 現在說太遲了 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然去踹機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是毫無關係的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫大家都被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我趁丸太你睡著的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了你的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是丸太你的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是生這個的氣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦 你快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待那裡的話很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣麼 我…又交到了新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:22.01,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}丸太 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 住手 你這塊破銅爛鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那個力量 使用那個力量的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現啊 出現啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不出現啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「利落」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「罪之枝」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一個擁有異世之力之人
